snippet: Britain's biggest online rail booking system Trainline is looking to list on the stock market in a move that could see the company valued at more than 400 million pounds ($680.72 million), Sky News reported....

headline.print_headline: UK Online Rail Booking System Trainline Looking to Launch an IPO-Sky
headline.main: UK Online Rail Booking System Trainline Looking to Launch an IPO-Sky

lead_paragraph: Britain's biggest online rail booking system Trainline is looking to list on the stock market in a move that could see the company valued at more than 400 million pounds ($680.72 million), Sky News reported.
